data.title: Digital Intelligent Operation
data.text:
Complete Vehicle Status Data

Over one hundred detailed vehicle data fields, including vehicle power consumption, wheel speed, battery, temperature and remaining mileage

Driver's Driving Behaviors

All-round driving behavior data, such as vehicle positioning, speed, accelerated speed, brake pedal opening and steering wheel angle

Travel Portraits

Form itinerary portrait, such as departure/destination, time, occurrence period, weather, etc.

Commercial Advertising

Implement mass information transfer through digital screens to provide passengers with personalized information display, local life services and so on

Intelligent Model

Intelligent Models

Through organic integration of multidimensional data, we develop a core algorithm model

Asset status

Real-time vehicle data display, maintenance reminder, online fault alarm and risk warning, residual asset value assessment and disposal prompts.
